===Noun===
'''gum arabic'''
{{wikipedia}}

#An edible substance taken from one of two species of sub-saharan [[acacia]] trees.  It is used in the food industry as a stabilizer (e.g. in [[soda]], [[gumdrops]] and [[marshmallows]]) and in other industries including pharmaceuticals, paints and polishs.

*also known as ''gum acacia''.